  // Generic activity log + itemised cost logs (MyFarm v2 loggers).
  // activities: land-prep/sowing/scout/weeding/pruning etc. {id,type,date,title,notes,photoUrl?,voiceUrl?,fields}
  // labor/expense/income logs carry {id,date,...,amountInr} — computeFinancials() sums these,
